### ============== USUÁRIOS ==============

### Listar todos os usuários
GET http://localhost:3000/usuarios

###

### Listar apenas alunos
GET http://localhost:3000/usuarios/alunos

###

### Criar novo aluno
POST http://localhost:3000/usuarios
content-type: application/json

{
  "nome": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@email.com",
  "senha": "senha123",
  "telefone": "11999999999"
}

###

### Criar admin
POST http://localhost:3000/usuarios
content-type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Maria Admin",
  "email": "maria.admin@email.com",
  "senha": "admin123",
  "telefone": "11988888888",
  "role": "admin"
}

###

### Autenticar usuário (admin de teste)
POST http://localhost:3000/usuarios/autenticacao
content-type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@renova.com",
  "senha": "admin123"
}

###

### Autenticar usuário (aluno de teste)
